{"word":"σαῦλος","slug":"σαῦλος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n93442\" key=\"sau=los\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">σαῦλος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">η</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, an <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adj.\">Adj.</a></pos> descriptive of gait and carriage, defined as <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὸ φαῦλον καὶ διερρυηκός</foreign> by Sch.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg004.perseus-grc1:1169\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ V.\">V.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1169</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σαῦλα ποσὶν βαίνουσα</foreign>, applied to the gait of the tortoise, <sense id=\"n93442.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">straddling, waddling,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">h.Merc.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">28</biblScope> </bibl>; of the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">loose, wanton</tr_> gait of courtesans or Bacchantes, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ς. βαίνειν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0237.tlg001:168\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Anacr.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">168</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σαῦλαι Βασσαρίδες</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0237.tlg001:55\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">55</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; also of a <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">prancing</tr_> horse, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ς. βαίνειν, ἵππος ὡς κορωνίης</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0260.tlg001:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Semon.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18</biblScope></bibl></cit>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}